y made some additional effort to help clients prevent future problems once they emerge from the debt settlement process. There is some useful information regarding the calculation of credit scores and how credit card companies calculate interest as well as a credit dictionary. Their website also offers an FAQ section but even it is rather limited to questions specifically geared towards their program. Customer support is provided by both email and telephone."]},"id":"fabc1797-0326-4bb6-a551-0333295f7a3e","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_3314","url":"/new-beginnings-debt-settlement-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"eli-mccormick","url":"/author/eli-mccormick","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Eli McCormick","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"CSoTtbWogSTgZ9Xgr3Anr9","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2009-06-30T15:48:49Z","datePublished":"2009-06-30T15:48:49Z","name":"New Beginnings Debt Settlement","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been discontinued.","review":{"rating":68,"verdict":"New Beginnings Debt Settlement offers a competitive debt settlement option with a well established firm.","pros":["Clients of New Beginnings can view the progress of their debt settlement plan on the company&#8217;s secure web site. "],"cons":["Credit counseling information offered by New Beginnings is quite limited. "]},"strapline":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been discontinued.","language":"en","dateModified":"2009-06-30T15:48:49Z","id":"sGSbdjDZKVXkQkxQEm9nU4","meta":{"title":"New Beginnings Debt Settlement Review - Pros and Cons","description":"For those who have determined that debt consolidation is necessary but the payments required for debt management are simply not possible, New Beginnings Debt Settlement offers a competitive de